{"tid":1956093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓累計過萬人確診　大邱市45日以來首次單位數增長","createTime":"2020-04-03T03:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T03:09:45.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"caf7ce65f0c6bbf15216bda1a2ab7e748183d4e7","tid":1956093,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T03:09:45.000Z","msg":"南韓確診感染新型肺炎病例突破一萬宗。當地疾控本部公布，過去一日新增86宗確診，增幅進一步放緩，累計10062人染病。另外再多5人染病後不治，令死亡人數增至174人。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社報道，首爾與周邊地區錄得40多宗新增確診病例。疫情重災區大邱市與慶尚北道，分別錄得9宗及5宗，是大邱市45日以來首次錄得單位數增幅。南韓在月初已經實施新的檢疫措施，要求所有入境的外國人士需隔離檢疫14日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518612-20200403.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518612-20200403.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BpuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=41475184\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518612-20200403.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=51f86985\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518612-20200403.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}